Test dataset for sample allocation from AllocSN

testData.Rd

This dataset is is a test dataset containing a small population of 100 companies. Variables include turnover for three periods and whethere they were sampled or not.

Usage

testData

Format

An object of class data.frame with 100 rows and 13 columns.

Value

One dataset containing 100 rows and 11 variables:

dufNr

company number

nace5

industry group (5 digits)

nace3

industry group (3 digits)

antAnsatt

number of employees in the first period

antAnsatt2

number of employees in the second period

storGrp

group for size of company based on number of employees in the first period

storGrp2

group for size of company based on number of employees in the second period

y1

turnover in the first period

y2

turnover in the second period

y3

turnover in the third period

utv1

binary variable for whether or not the company was in the sample for the first period

utv2

binary variable for whether or not the company was in the sample for the second period

utv3

binary variable for whether or not the company was in the sample for the third period
